# Stellar Game - Code Standards

## Quick Reference

- **Laravel Sail**: Always use `./vendor/bin/sail` for all commands (artisan, composer, npm, etc.) to ensure consistency with the Docker development environment
- **Chrome DevTools MCP**: Use Chrome DevTools MCP to visually verify the application after launching or implementing new features (take snapshot, check console errors, verify network requests)
- **Blade Layouts**: All Blade views rendered by controllers MUST use `@extends('layouts.app')` or appropriate layout. Livewire components use `#[Layout('layouts.app')]` attribute
- **Laravel Pint**: Use `./vendor/bin/sail pint` for formatting
- **Tests**: Write tests for new features
- **Form Requests**: Use FormRequest for API validation
- **Migrations**: Use Laravel migrations (not raw SQL)
- **API-first**: All business logic via REST API endpoints
- **Event-driven**: Use Laravel events for business logic

